room_title: Escape room "Boat Break" by Amaze: The Columbus Escape Experience in Columbus
review: 10 out of 10, we'll come back again! The experiences are well-designed and the staff is excellent. My husband and I were the only two in our party for the boat experience. We had a great time! Can't wait to try one of their other offerings.
